\|x+y\|^2=\langle x+y, x+y\rangle=\langle x, x\rangle+2\langle x, y\rangle+\langle y, y\rangle,
\|x+y\|^2\leq \langle x, x\rangle +2\langle x,x\rangle^{1/2}\langle y, y\rangle^{1/2}+\langle y,y\rangle= (\|x\|+\|y\|)^2,
